Date><ingested> 1692209186</ingested><modified> 2023-08-16T18:06:34+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Billy Steele]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/aa7d1b40-3c50-11ee-8fdb-2b4f84bf2a74" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/aa7d1b40-3c50-11ee-8fdb-2b4f84bf2a74" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Solo Stove/Matthew King]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Solo Stove Pi Prime]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Solo Stove Pi Prime]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Steam Remote Play now officially supports 4K gaming]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Valve 刚刚<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/group/4397053?emclan=103582791433918461&amp;emgid=5651507201768194518"><ins>发布了 Steam 客户端测试版更新</ins></a>，最终引入了一项广受欢迎的功能。 Steam 远程游戏服务现将提供 4K 支持，并提供一系列预设，让游戏玩家能够为喜爱的游戏找到完美的高分辨率设置。在此更新之前，远程播放时仍然可以使用 4K，但需要对设置进行大量实验，并且并不总是能正常工作。这应该可以解决其中许多问题。</p><p>这一举措让游戏玩家在进行远程流媒体游戏时最终可以利用 4K 显示器等高端外围设备。对于新手来说，Steam Remote Play 是一项有用的服务，可将 PC 游戏从 Steam 库传输到手机、平板电脑、笔记本电脑和相关设备。它的兄弟服务 Steam Remote Play Together 增加了在线多人游戏功能，实际上允许没有游戏的玩家<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/steam-remote-play-together-out-of-beta-070308920.html"><ins>加入竞争或合作游戏。</ins></a></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> 4K 流媒体并不是此更新中包含的唯一新功能，但它肯定是最引人注目的。 Valve 现在还允许用户调整设置窗口的大小，并且在进行细微调整（例如摆弄 4K 流）时，它使后退按钮更加可靠。该公司还修复了一大堆错误，例如验证游戏安装时未重新创建文件夹以及显示文件对话框时覆盖冻结。</p><p>最后，大图片模式修复了一些小错误，Steam 增加了对印度尼西亚语的支持。该更新现已可供下载，但这<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://help.steampowered.com/en/faqs/view/276C-85A0-C531-AFA3"><ins>是测试版</ins></a>，因此您可能需要等到正式的最终版本。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/steam-remote-play-now-officially-supports-4k-gaming-182020228.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/steam-remote-play-now-officially-supports-4k-gaming-182020228.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 000aa9b5-5ada-4473-b04c-7847bbe293f5</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 16 Aug 2023 18:20:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692209430</ingested><modified> 2023-08-16T18:10:41+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="2560" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/10b1d8e0-3c5d-11ee-b5df-9d239e978a74" width="3792"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2560" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/10b1d8e0-3c5d-11ee-b5df-9d239e978a74" width="3792"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_ht